Package com.sun.identity.saml.plugins

SAML 1.x Plugins.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionMapper
    The class ActionMapper is an interface that is implemented to get SSO information and map partner actions to OpenSSO authorization decisions.
    AttributeMapper
    The class AttributeMapper is an interface that is implemented to get SSO information and map partner attributes to OpenSSO attributes.
    ConsumerSiteAttributeMapper
    This interface needs to be implemented by an trusted assertion consumer site (a partner) to return a list of Attribute objects to be returned as AttributeStatements elements, as part of the Authentication Assertion returned to the partner during the SSO scenario of Browser Artifact and POST profile.
    NameIdentifierMapper
    The class NameIdentifierMapper is an interface that is implemented to map user account to name identifier in assertion subject in OpenSSO.
    PartnerAccountMapper
    The class PartnerAccountMapper is an interface that is implemented to map partner account to user account in OpenSSO.
    PartnerSiteAttributeMapper Deprecated
    This class has been deprecated.
    SiteAttributeMapper Deprecated
    This class has been deprecated.
